description:

If you are new to Windows 10, you need this book. Form new security features to organization, this book will help you navigate the newest form of operating systems. You will learn how to use the registry and so much more. No matter if you have upgraded your computer during the free year or you have purchased a full copy, this book will help you get started and even be there when you have to reinstall the operating system should you need to.

Windows 10: The Ultimate Guide for Beginners to Operate Microsoft Windows 10
